To install, place the script in your OmniFocus User Scripts folder:

    /Users/<username>/Libarary/Scripts/Applications/OmniFocus

Then, right click on the OmniFocus toolbar and click `Customize Toolbar...` Drag the item called `Script: Copy as Markdown` onto your toolbar.

To use, select one or more actions and click the button!

